page.title: 09Moy Child
page.content:
I am 10 years old. My birth sign is Libra. I have brown hair and blue eyes. There are 6 people in my family. I have a mum and a dad, two brothers and one sister. I have lived in Moy all my life. When I have any spare time I play. I like watching the A Team and Robin Hood on television. My favourite food is fruit. My favourite colour is black. I have several friends. Dad works in a quarry. I wouldn't mind any job if it had a lot of money. I don't know if I would have to leave Moy for work. I like living in Moy.
PETS IN MOY _ 23 dogs 15 cats 14 gerbils 1 guinea pig 3 ferrets LOCAL ROAD NAMES _ Birch Walk Black's Road Danny's Brae Farm Road Macs Drive Tower Road
